responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "A59A707B47A98664316F359D5D40D9C0", "A joyful time this year, ain\'t it? It\'s like these folks can\'t go home without sporting a few bruises to chase their drink. Nothing better to bring the hounds around than a fresh batch of moonshine. Say, I haven\'t seen your face around here. Are you here for the big show?")
